chess.logic.chessboardinitializers

Class ChessBoardInitializer

  • java.lang.Object
    • chess.logic.chessboardinitializers.ChessBoardInitializer
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    EmptyBoardInitializer, StandardBoardInitializer

    public abstract class ChessBoardInitializer
extends Object
    All classes that inherit this abstract class are used to initialize different starting situations on chessboard like empty board or standard starting positions.
    Author:
    sami
